No. 301,

Misc.

Green v. Clancy, U. S. District Judge, et al. Blanch Freedman and Gloria Agrin for petitioner. Jacob K. Javits, Attorney General of New York, James O. Moore, Jr., Solicitor General, and Daniel M. Cohen and Irving L. Rollins, Assistant Attorneys General, for Javits et al., respondents.
